&lt;h3&gt;About the role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are looking for a DevOps Engineer to own build and deployment automation for Vannevar Labs. Your decisions today will have a large impact on the company’s future. We believe that simple systems are easier to understand, maintain, and scale. You will be making trade-offs as you work to ensure that our systems are prepared to operate in both commercial and high-side environments at scale — being able to effectively communicate these trade-offs with your teammates is a must.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, maintain, and be responsible for overall platform health, scaling and planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing self-service tools and automating things to improve data engineering efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build logging and monitoring tools to visualize the state of the platform and improve our SRE practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play a critical part in implementing a secure, robust and high availability DevOps pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the team to continue the build out of a multi-account AWS environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate build &amp;amp; deployment processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in DevOps, software engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience crafting CI/CD processes and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge in AWS cloud technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with PLG stack, Datadog, or other enterprise monitoring tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with infrastructure as code technologies such as Terraform and Pulumi.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient with containerization technologies like Docker.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent with Python, Bash, or other scripting languages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in an agile scrum environment and also an ability to work independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to quickly learn new and existing technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and excellent analytical capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;U.S. Citizenship status is required as this position will require the ability to access U.S. only data systems and export-controlled data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TS Clearance preferred or must be willing to obtain clearance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
