&lt;p&gt;Secure access is a critical enabler of Vannevar’s mission. We are seeking an Engineering Manager to lead the Security Platform team and drive the strategy, execution, and evolution of the systems that govern authentication, authorization, and access management across our products. In this role, you will lead a team responsible for centralized identity and access infrastructure, including IdP integrations, authorization policy frameworks, SSO capabilities, and access management tooling. Working closely with engineering, mission, and product partners, you will build secure-by-default platforms that reduce friction for developers, provide clarity and control for administrators, and ensure end users can access only the resources they are authorized to see.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Grow and mentor a high-performing team of engineers. Foster a strong engineering culture focused on security, reliability, ownership, and delivering high-impact platform capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategy and technical direction:&lt;/strong&gt; Define the roadmap and technical vision for authentication, authorization, and access management capabilities, ensuring Vannevar’s identity platform scales securely and reliably with the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform and developer enablement:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the development of centralized identity and access services—including IdP integrations, authorization infrastructure, and SSO capabilities—that reduce friction for product teams and enable secure-by-default development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-functional execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Product, Mission, Infrastructure, and Engineering teams to deliver foundational identity and access capabilities that balance security, usability, and operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organizational impact:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive adoption of access control standards, security best practices, and platform capabilities across engineering teams to create a consistent and trustworthy access experience throughout Vannevar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What we’re looking for&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engineering leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; 3+ years of experience leading and developing high-performing software engineering teams, with a track record of delivering complex technical initiatives and growing engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
