&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end technical delivery for your mission workstreams, from requirements gathering and system design through implementation, deployment, and sustainment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute hands-on code to improve product capabilities, performance, and scalability across customer use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build software that enables users to unlock value from large-scale data holdings, including text, multimedia, and geospatial datasets spanning over 46 languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional partners — including engineers, product designers, and mission domain experts — to plan and deliver complex software features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support government-facing technical artifacts as needed, including input to RFIs, RFPs, Statements of Work, and white papers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate and integrate with government IT ecosystems, ensuring solutions meet security, compliance, and operational constraints&lt;/li&gt;
